sentences.sentence: Happy tines are fun to share!
sentences.translation: 分享愉快的时光是多么的有趣！

sentences.sentence: The difference is that you keep the fork in your left hand to take the food to your mouth but with the tines down.
sentences.translation: 所以说唯一的区别是，叉子不换到右手上，一直是左手拿叉，吃的时候叉子的尖儿冲下。

sentences.sentence: Im sorry that I cant be with you on this Valentines Day. I send this Valen tines card to remind you that I love you.
sentences.translation: 很抱歉，这个情人节我不能陪你。我送上这张卡片，为的是要提示你，我爱你。
